.DT
learn
Discworld player help
learn

Name
.SI 5
learn - Learn skills from someone
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
learn <skill> from <person>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This enables you to learn a skill that a person has offered to teach you.
You can also teach yourself a skill but this is much more expensive
than getting someone else to teach you.  To teach yourself a skill
you learn a skill from yourself.  You may only teach yourself one
level at a time.
.EP

Examples
.SI 5
> learn fighting from pinkfish
You learn 2 levels of fighting from Pinkfish for 5000 xp.
.EI

See also:
.SI 5
teach, skills
.EI
